channel.title: Dodian Basic Source Great for begginers
channel.description:
Hi!
Today i will release source called "dodian basic source".This source is great for begginers or somebody who want to start again.Only what you need to do is change things like name:your server name change to yours.And shops are there to but you need to add stuffs in there.Help with Shop maker you can find my post down there at server downloads. ;D
http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?3i2ttjy3jgy http://uppit.com/v/9Q1TNLN4
Home: [img]http://i40.tinypic.com/m9amg1.jpg[/img]
Dragon Cave: [img]http://i42.tinypic.com/10ho8ba.jpg[/img]
Shops:[img]http://i44.tinypic.com/x7hh0.jpg[/img]
This is not my source i have found it at my programs but questions are welcome :D Rebornscape
COMMENT + RATE PLEASE TO KEEP THIS TOPIC ALIVE :rolleyes:
